Chan AL(1), Leung HW, Huang SF.

Author information:
(1)Department of Pharmacy, Chi Mei Medical Center, Tainan, Taiwan.

BACKGROUND: Concomitant chemotherapy with radiotherapy is considered to be the 
standard of care for patients with head and neck cancer and good performance 
